WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Today, we will focus on product costing.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Now that SMH ensures SAP has complete and consistent production data, the next step is making use of that data by turning it into insights.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.000
And that is where SAP Joule comes in.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:23.000
Once operational data is integrated into SAP, organizations can unlock a new level of intelligence using SAP Joule.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:31.000
Joule is SAP’s enterprise AI copilot, designed to help users quickly analyze business data and identify insights.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:41.000
By connecting SAP Joule with PDF Operational Product Costing analytics, users can instantly analyze manufacturing performance and product costing.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:48.000
Within seconds, Joule can identify key operational cost drivers and highlight the areas that require attention.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:53.000
Now let’s apply it. Using the Newest Product Costing Demo flow with real SAP Joule prompts and responses.